name: xeniumranger

variants.name: build_system
variants.description: Build systems supported by the package

description:
The Xenium In Situ software suite is a set of software applications for
analyzing and visualizing in situ gene expression data produced by the
Xenium Analyzer. Xenium Ranger provides flexible off-instrument
reanalysis of Xenium In Situ data. This package requires the user to
accept a license and to download the tarball manually. Once downloaded,
the file should be placed within a manual mirror or within the current
directory. For instructions on making a manual mirror, see
https://spack.readthedocs.io/en/latest/mirrors.html
